 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A braai with a pap bake is the real McCoy. The pap bake can be made the day before and just put in the oven on the day of the braai. You can give a pap bake various flavours and tastes.  It's just like a kiss &#8211; you kiss as you please. It stays delicious!</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-049.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-049-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"pap blog 049\" class=\"wp-image-982\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>",
