  "ingredientsTitle": "Ingredients",
  "ingredientGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "items": [
     "3 cups maize meal <br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-023.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-023-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 023\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "3 cups milk",
     "4 cups water",
     "60ml butter",
     "1 packet bacon",
     "1 onion sliced into rings<br>",
     "30 ml oil<br>",
     "1 tin tomato and onion mix<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-011.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-011-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 011\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "10 ml mixed herbs<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-014.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-014-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 014\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "4 cheese grillers (if you have them, otherwise leave them out)",
     "1 tin whole kernel corn<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-027.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-027-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 027\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "2 cups grated cheese of your choice<br>",
     "salt and pepper"
    ]
   }
  ],
  "directionsTitle": "Method",
  "directionGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "steps": [
     "Fry the onions in 30 ml oil.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-002.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-002.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 002\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Chop the bacon and fry it together with the onions.",
     "Slice the grillers into rings and fry them along with the bacon.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-003.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-003.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 003\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Stir in 10ml mixed herbs and the tin of tomato mix and cook through for 10 minutes &#8211; then set the mixture aside.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-016.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-016.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 016\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Heat the milk and water in a pot.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-021.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-021.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 021\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Add the maize meal, salt and pepper and stir so it doesn't form lumps &#8211; let it simmer for 15 minutes.",
     "Stir the butter into the pap.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-030.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-030.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 030\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Stir the whole kernel corn into the pap.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-034.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-034.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 034\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Grease an ovenproof dish and spoon a layer of pap into the bottom of the dish.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-037.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-037.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 037\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Followed by a layer of the bacon and onion mixture.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-038.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-038.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 038\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Followed by a layer of cheese, repeat the layers once more.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-041.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-041.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 041\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Finish right at the top with a layer of cheese.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-046.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 046\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Bake it for 40 minutes at 180 degrees Celsius.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-047.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-047.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 047\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>"
    ]
   }
  ],
  "notesTitle": "Notes",
  "notes": [
   "You can use any filling you like. The bacon can be replaced with vegetables. I used an aniseed cheese in the pap bake. The choice of cheese also comes down to personal preference. I've even made this bake with delicious blue cheese."
  ],
